g":"最後一點大逆不道啊屍永青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcb34ec2cd98b0843ea5f7f76aa9800732aff27","tid":1589900,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"奶共友緊係想支共千秋萬世"},{"pid":"e2179a31ec6305ec7b90d3ad6a6056a6e69404ff","tid":1589900,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"419b20df36d6c6cf74dcf99fd51fd9e845d89e11","tid":1589900,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"同埋一個人答唔到你問題<br />\n可能係件事太複雜，佢未必即時醒得起去答你<br />\n亦唔代表佢反政府係炒車架喎<br />\n<br />\n反而覺得施生成日話人係錯，咁佢可唔可以提供一個方法係「一定掂」<br />\n當然係以佢精準嘅眼光，相信可能都畀到我地一啲意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"佢上次都講出口，一定掂既方法就係親共，佢話起碼到佢死果日中共都係到"},{"pid":"dd7baa918664cf3c504ef71a8950f92e1511d3ef","tid":1589900,"uid":315190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0930784bc2875872b5ef57799fd3995470fb5c","tid":1589900,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6247183ee4d3e3ad79d726ca3cc8e21404a2666","tid":1589900,"uid":160348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f0acc223596fb7418c910abb6d04d1c9ec06571","tid":1589900,"uid":93986,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:01:48.000Z","msg":"因此，要達致這項訴求，非要推翻中共政權不可。<br />\n<br />\n施永青想煽動群眾革命？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"擺明啦。佢一向主張推得冧共產黨佢就有興趣加入<br />\n<br />\n佢唔埋黃絲堆係因為佢覺得中共冇咁快收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"典型牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8167120a4d178bd75674ac46b8e80068b4ecfe38","tid":1589900,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":